  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients undergoing otorhinolaryngologic surgery, unknown Staphylococcus aureus
             carriage state

          -  Patient affiliated to French Social Security

          -  Written consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Antibiotherapy or infectious episode during the month prior enrollment

          -  coagulation disorder

          -  neoplasia of the nasal cavity
      </textblock>
